task4.sentences.tar.gz 

 - contains a file for each topic. Each such file contains only the
relevant sentences from the documents associated with that topic (see
topic file for the list of those documents). The sentences are ordered
first by the ranking of the document they came from and within that by
the sequence in which they appeared in that document. The relevant
sentences which were deemed novel (when read in the order given) are
tagged NOVEL.
